  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-02 adversarial sample)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed. This package is a synthetic adversarial sample targeting W-EP-02: one ValidationResult carries a detailed narrative describing its generating experiment but omits the structured prov:wasGeneratedBy activity link, creating a provenance gap that a reviewer might overlook because the prose appears sufficient.",
